<li>
<i><a href="/wiki/The_Twenty_Years%27_Crisis" title="The Twenty Years' Crisis">The Twenty Years' Crisis</a>, 1919–1939: an Introduction to the Study of International Relations</i>, London: Macmillan, 1939, revised edition, 1946.</li>
